        <content type="html" xml:base="https://joshafairhead.com/tea-blog/assam-tgfop/">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;joshafairhead.com&#x2F;tea-blog&#x2F;assam-tgfop&#x2F;image1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Assam Tgfop packet&quot; &#x2F;&gt;
